      • pageChanged

        void pageChanged(java.lang.Object changedProperty)
        Utility method invoked when ever interested views/components should update themselves to reflect the latest state of the editor.

        This method can also be invoked programatically using YRCBaseBehavior.pageChanged() .

        This method is invoked by infrastructure in the following scernarios:
        • Editor gets focus.
        • New task is shown in an editor.
        • New wizard page is shown with in a currently running task.
        See Also:
        YRCBaseBehavior.pageChanged(String)
